  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:3",
      "text": "课程的四个 Glow shaders，使其能够用 Primvar 控制 PxrSurface Glow Intensity。完成后，我们就能使用一些巧妙的 VEX code 来控制 neons 的 animation。",
      "ascii_letters": 62,
      "cjk_chars": 30
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:4",
      "text": "USD Asset Setup（USD 资产设置）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:5",
      "text": "我们想要的是动态控制 neon tubes 的“chasing” animation。",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:7",
      "text": "editmaterialproperties",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:9",
      "text": "在第一个 Glow Shader 内，创建一个 PrimVar node，将 Variable type 保持为 Float，但一定要把 Float value 设置为 0.1。这会给我们一个初始 intensity value。",
      "ascii_letters": 62,
      "cjk_chars": 30
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:11",
      "text": "然后把 Primvar 的 resultR 连接到 PxrSurface 的 glowgain。",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:14",
      "text": "Outer_INT",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:16",
      "text": "Inner_INT",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:17",
      "text": "White_INT",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:18",
      "text": "完成后，需要重新 publish USD asset，然后把它 reload 到我们的 main network 中。",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:19",
      "text": "Time to Animate!（开始制作动画！）",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:21",
      "text": "Start：先创建一个 AttributeWrangle node，并把下面的 code 粘贴到 VEXpression box 中。",
      "ascii_letters": 43,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:28",
      "text": "每个 neon 保持 OFF 的 frames 数",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:30",
      "text": "neons 保持 ON 的 frames 数",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:31",
      "text": "Transition",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:32",
      "text": "向上/向下渐变（ramp up / ramp down）所需的 frames 数",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:33",
      "text": "FrameOffset",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:34",
      "text": "更改这个 value 可调整所有 neons 之间的 offset time",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:35",
      "text": "Intensity",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:36",
      "text": "neons 应达到的最大 intensity",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:39",
      "text": "你的 surfaces 里的 glowgain 参数，",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "1ba1aaf396:41",
      "text": "感谢 Pixar 的 Damien Maupu 提供这段很酷的 VFX code！",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    }
  ],
